<H1><img align=middle alt="" src="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~arcadia/Icons/arcadia-logo.gif">
The Arcadia Consortium</H1>
<HR>

The Arcadia project is organized as an informal consortium of separately
funded researchers.  These include the following academic institutions
and principal investigators:

<H2><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/Arcadia/atUCI.html">
Arcadia at University of California, Irvine (UCI)</A></H2>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<DL>
<DT> <STRONG><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/dir/faculty/Software/djr"> Debra J. Richardson</A></STRONG> (djr@ics.uci.edu)
<DD> Testing, Analysis
<DT> <STRONG>Richard W. Selby</STRONG> (selby@ics.uci.edu)
<DD> Measurement and Evaluation
<DT> <STRONG><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/dir/faculty/Software/taylor"> Richard N. Taylor</A></STRONG> (taylor@ics.uci.edu)
<DD> Software Architecture, User Interface Software, Team-Support Software,
and Hypermedia
</DL>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

